How to play:
Use your mouse to look around and point in the direction you would like to travel.

Use W, S, A, & D for movement.
 - W to move forward 
 - S to move backwards
 - A to move to the left 
 - D to move to the right

Use alphanumeric 3 & 4 to enable the light.
 - 3 to turn the light on
 - 4 to turn the light off